    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>KOPELOV--Jean, on January 4th, 2007. Beloved wife of the late David. Devoted mother of Jill (Len) Berman, cherished grandmother of Michael, Daniel, and Rachel. Services will be held on Sunday January 7th, 2007 at 10AM at the Riverside-Nassau North Chapels, 55 North Station Plaza (opposite LIRR), Great Neck, NY. Interment to follow at The Hungarian Union Fields Cemetery.</p>
      </block>
